    "body": "@tejohnso `nodeIntegration` is not the only problem, the webview element gives the parent page complete control over the renderer webview page.  That kind of power should not be given out lightly.  Imagine a random website X being rendered in Electron just throwing up a webview for the google sign in screen but injecting JS to capture the password.  Entirely possible if they access to the webview element.  The current model is safe and I don't think it should change."
  },
